org.deeplearning4j.zoo.model

Class Darknet19

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.zoo.ZooModel
      • org.deeplearning4j.zoo.model.Darknet19
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InstantiableModel

    public class Darknet19
extends ZooModel
    Darknet19 Reference: https://arxiv.org/pdf/1612.08242.pdf

    ImageNet weights for this model are available and have been converted from https://pjreddie.com/darknet/imagenet/ using https://github.com/allanzelener/YAD2K .

    There are 2 pretrained models, one for 224x224 images and one fine-tuned for 448x448 images. Call setInputShape() with either {3, 224, 224} or {3, 448, 448} before initialization. The channels of the input images need to be in RGB order (not BGR), with values normalized within [0, 1]. The output labels are as per https://github.com/pjreddie/darknet/blob/master/data/imagenet.shortnames.list .
